{"tid":1496249,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲有邊緣型人格障礙","createTime":"2019-08-22T12:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T20:24:14.000Z","uid":57397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a11ea4cbc307fac91ec5aba80f1be11ed394c8e","tid":1496249,"uid":57397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c92b89ccfa0b98df664bead1610899e6bde3491","tid":1496249,"uid":57397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"美國精神醫學會出版的診斷手冊(DSM-5)，以下九項症狀，如符合五項以上,即是診斷邊緣人格的主要依據之一：<br />\n<br />\n    無法忍受被人拋棄，一旦發生，會有激烈反應。<br />\n    極端的思考模式，是非對錯以自己的認知為中心，極易造成人際衝突。<br />\n    有自我認同障礙，自信心低或過度自信，因此影響人際關係。<br />\n    情緒低落時，會有自我傷害及放縱的行為，例如：飆車、瘋狂購物、傷害他人的衝動。<br />\n    會藉由輕生、自殘等威脅他人不得結束情感關係。例如：情殺。<br />\n    不合時宜的爆發憤怒情緒，或對憤怒難以控制，例如：校園傷害槍擊恐嚇。<br />\n    情緒失控時，憂鬱、焦慮情緒會持續數小時。<br />\n    害怕孤單，經常有空虛感。<br />\n    在瞬變中，出現與壓力有關的妄想，或嚴重解離現象。"},{"pid":"3dbce351defa216e85195f2b351941a92660e944","tid":1496249,"uid":75318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:26:51.000Z","msg":"你有？"},{"pid":"de1e2633028082f108792d146563576fae0a9dda","tid":1496249,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"留名聽分享"},{"pid":"9dd01bbd01fb2abeca0df8966242b25c3bf64cf6","tid":1496249,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"似警犬性格"},{"pid":"dfcf0513063f13c71b2429d874657dcb5bf43204","tid":1496249,"uid":278506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"me...."},{"pid":"aac825be5da14964bcfa40294fb3a4da9098eb6f","tid":1496249,"uid":253135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:36:28.000Z","msg":"me..."},{"pid